name: Bondi Sands Aero Self Tanning Foam 225Ml
breadcrumbs: Home ~ Health & Beauty ~ Body Skincare ~ Fake Tan
description:
Product Description

  • bondisands.com.au
  • Experience the next generation in self tan with Bondi Sands Aero, an Aerated Self Tanning Foam. With dual tanning actives and our signature coconut scent, this ultra lightweight aerosol foam will leave your skin with a deep, long lasting bronzed glow.
  • Dual Action Formula Bondi Sands innovative dual action tanning formula provides a deep, long lasting natural look tan that hydrates the skin with every application.
  • The Australian tan
  • Quick dry formula
  • Intense hydration
  • Coconut scent
  • Australian made
  • Not tested on animals
  • Pack size: 225ML

Information

Ingredients

Aqua (Water), Alcohol, Propylene Glycol, Dihydroxyacetone, Butane, Dimethyl Isosorbide, Glycerin, Propane, Ethoxydiglycol, PEG-60 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Polysorbate 20, Parfum (Fragrance), Erythrulose, CI 14700 (FD&C Red No. 4), CI 19140 (FD&C Yellow No. 5), Hydrolyzed Jojoba Esters, CI 42090 (FD&C Blue No. 1), Bisabolol, Tocopheryl Acetate, Farnesol, Coumarin, Propellant: Hydrocarbon

Produce of

Made in Australia

Preparation and Usage

  • Step 1 For an even streak free tan, ensure your skin is clean, exfoliated and free of any moisturisers.
  • Step 2 Apply Bondi Sands Aero liberally to a tanning mitt before using a long sweeping motion to legs, arms and body. Use remaining residue on tanning mitt for face, elbows and knees.
  • Step 3 Leave on skin for at least 6 hours. Shower with warm water and gently pat skin dry. For the deepest tan re-apply Bondi Sands Aero 30 minutes after initial application.

Warnings

  • FOR EXTERNAL USE ONLY. This product does not contain a sunscreen and does not protect against sunburn. Repeated exposure of unprotected skin while tanning may increase the risk of skin aging, skin cancer and other harmful effects to the skin even if you do not burn.
  • KEEP OUT OF THE SIGHT AND REACH OF CHILDREN. Test on a small area. Do no apply to damaged, inflamed or sensitive skin. If irritation, redness or itchiness occurs, discontinue use. If swallowed, get medical attention or contact a Poison Control Centre right away. Keep away from eyes. If material accidentally enters the eye, rinse well with plenty of clean water. Seek medical attention if irritation persists.
  • WARNING: CONTENTS UNDER PRESSURE. DO NOT PUNCTURE OR INCINERATE. DO NOT STORE AT TEMPERATURE ABOVE 120°F. KEEP OUT OF REACH OF CHILDREN. USE ONLY AS DIRECTED. INTENTIONAL MISUSE BY DELIBERATELY CONCENTRATING AND INHALING THE CONTENTS CAN BE HARMFUL OR FATAL.
  • DANGER: EXTREMELY FLAMMABLE AEROSOL. PRESSURISED CONTAINER: MAY BURST IF HEATED. KEEP AWAY FROM HEAT, HOT SURFACES, SPARKS, OPEN FLAMES AND OTHER IGNITION SOURCES. NO SMOKING. DO NOT SPRAY ON AN OPEN FLAME OR OTHER IGNITION SOURCE. DO NOT PIERCE OR BURN, EVEN AFTER USE. PROTECT FROM SUNLIGHT. DO NOT EXPOSE TO TEMPERATURES EXCEEDING 50°C/122°F. SOLVENT ABUSE CAN KILL INSTANTLY.

name: Skinny Tan Gradual Tanner 125Ml
breadcrumbs: Home ~ Health & Beauty ~ Body Skincare ~ Fake Tan
description:
• Suitable for vegans
  • Suitable for vegetarians

Product Description

  • Skinny Tan Gradual Tanner 125ml
  • SkinnyTan™ Gradual Tanner (Bronzant Progressif) is a coconut-scented moisturising cream that builds a natural looking tan. It goes on clear and includes a naturally derived tanning agent that is kind to the skin. No orange, no streaking, no nasty smell and all the goodness of SkinnyTan™ smoothing oils and skin conditioning Guarana Seed Extract.
  • SkinnyTan™ is a registered trademark of SkinnyTan™ UK Ltd.
  • Everyday tanning lotion that gradually builds your tan
  • Packed with hydrating aloe vera
  • Delicious coconut scent
  • Streak Free Self Tanner
  • Naturally Derived Tanning Agent
  • Suitable for Vegans & Vegetarians
  • Pack size: 125ML

Information

Ingredients

Aqua (Water), Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil, Dihydroxyacetone, Cetearyl Alcohol, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Glyceryl Stearate, PEG-100 Stearate, Hydroxyethylcellulose, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Juice, Paullinia Cupana (Guarana) Seed Extract, Ethylhexylglycerin, Citric Acid, Parfum (Fragrance), Phenoxyethanol, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate

Storage

Store in a cool dry place under 15°C / 59°F.

Produce of

Made in the U.K.

Preparation and Usage

  • Directions:
  • 1. Exfoliate skin using our SkinnyTan™ Pre-Tan Primer and Exfoliating Mitt for a streak-free, even tan.
  • 2. Ensure skin is completely clean and dry prior to application.
  • 3. Apply as you would a normal body lotion.
  • 4. Wash hands with warm, soapy water directly after application.
  • 5. Allow time to dry.
  • 6. Dress and go.
  • 7. Re-apply until you reach your desired level of tan.
  • Note: Shake well before use. Gradual Tanner goes on clear so the developing colour is a true indication of the colour you will achieve. Tan takes 6-8 hours to completely develop.

Warnings

  • WARNING:
  • For external use only. Keep out of reach of children. In case of contact with eyes, rinse immediately with clean water. This product does not contain a sunscreen and does not protect against sunburn. Repeated exposure of unprotected skin while tanning may increase the risk of skin ageing and skin cancer.
